CoraJadeV1 Textual Inversion

файл на civitaiстраница на civitai

Hey there, this is my first ti. It recreates images of wrestler Cora Jade. The idea to create this ti came from a friend who asked me to generate pictures of her in SD but without the ti I couldn't get decent images. The first few tries where a total disaster and I didn't touch the files in much. But thanks to JernauGurgeh and his help I was able to get the process done. So many thanks to them! Most of the prompts show here to generate the images are basically theirs too. :D

Any feedback is welcome!

NataLee

файл на civitaiстраница на civitai

Natalie Lee, better known as NataLee, Instagram model and influencer.

I thought it was about time I gave my very first embedding a paint-job. When I created it, I thought it was a poor attempt because I didn't really know how TIs worked and I was building pretty poor prompts. In retrospect, I now think it was at least a very decent TI, and I'm not really sure this new version improves upon it. I'll let you judge.

The new version is an 1800-step TI. I removed 5 pics from the original dataset of 23 to leave it at 18, and applied my usual settings.

bad_pictures

файл на civitaiстраница на civitai

A very versatile negative embedding that helps generate high quality images. Higher chances of producing normal looking hands in realistic images.

Best Practices:

Keep your token usage to below 75 for best effect. Most of the time, you don't need to add other quality specifiers to your prompts (e.g. worst quality, bad quality).

Usage:

Negative prompt: file_name_of_embedding

If you notice any artifacts, you can try increasing or decreasing the weighting like this: (file_name_of_embedding:1.1) or [file_name_of_embedding:0.8].

Values between 0.8 and 1.2 seems to work the best (clip size 2):

Tested on:

  • VersaMix

  • ChilloutMix

  • Grapefruit
